OOc:  This was tottaly made up by me and Rhinox
 
the hakunians are a warlike transformers race. there are 4 major factions. they are the tripa, the tropons, the destructions and the beaters. would like your ok on this before i bring it into the group.  
the hakunians are a warlike transformers race. there are 4 major factions. they are the tripa, the tropons, the destructions and the beaters. (you can change the names of them if u want to). the tripa, the tropons are likely to to ally withe the maxis/autobots while the destructions and the beaters are likely to be allied with the preds/decipticons. 
 
The actual tranformers have 5 modes two beast, two viechle and a robot mode.


the faction part of the Hakunains will wait for now. if you are to have a hakunain charr for the time being they will have to be part of the preds, maxis, tripeds or the other factions. if they are preds they are part of the 
destructions and the beaters  factions while if they join the maxis they are part of  the tripa, the tropons factions. and they cannot change from good to bad  or vice versa no matter how much u want them two. if u try the char will self destruct.
